Print results from SLOPE fit

Source: R/print.R
print.SLOPE.Rd

Print results from SLOPE fit

# S3 method for SLOPE
print(x, ...)

# S3 method for TrainedSLOPE
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

an object of class 'SLOPE' or 'TrainedSLOPE'
...

other arguments passed to print()

Value

Prints output on the screen

Examples

fit <- SLOPE(wine$x, wine$y, family = "multinomial")
print(fit, digits = 1)
